.SS Notes on colors
.TP
.B Opacity for rgba and hsla Styles
For
.BR rgba " and " hsla
values, the
.RB \(lq a \(rq
refers to the color's opacity.  The range of values
is from 0 to 100, with 0 being fully transparent and 100 being
fully opaque.
.TP
.B Color Names
The collection of CSS color names are recognized for the color
portion of the
.B content
part of the URL.  A link to a CSS color table can be found below.

